metaTitle: Reset Restart Refocus Refill Coffee by Tobe Fonseca | Tobe Fonseca's Artist Shop
metaDescription: A coffee cup spills endlessly, forming an infinity symbol made of flowing coffee. This artwork celebrates the endless cycle of energy, focus, and motivation that keeps us going. Perfect for coffee lovers, caffeine addicts, and anyone who believes that every restart begins with a refill.
